query_relationships -  This method returns the relationships the selected person has to the other people in the family.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
class relationship_data * query_relationships(string name,
string person)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the family
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the person who to query the relationships for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the list of all the relationships the person has

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/inherit/club_family.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the relationships the selected person has to
the other people in the family.
